<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,405,431]" pageId="13" pageNumber="499">Remarks.</emphasis>
First record for 
<collectingCountry box="[505,605,405,431]" name="Hungary" pageId="13" pageNumber="499">Hungary</collectingCountry>
. This species is widely distributed and known from the Palaearctic (both Western and Eastern) and Oriental regions (
<bibRefCitation author="Yu, D. S. &amp; van Achterberg, C. &amp; Horstmann, K." box="[640,804,440,467]" pageId="13" pageNumber="499" refId="ref10079" refString="Yu, D. S., van Achterberg, C. &amp; Horstmann, K. (2012) Taxapad 2012 - World Ichneumonoidea 2011. Taxonomy, Biology, Morphology and Distribution. Ottawa, Ontario. Available from: http: // www. taxapad. com (accessed 12 January 2020)" type="url" year="2012">
Yu 
<emphasis box="[680,729,440,466]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="499">et al</emphasis>
. 2012
</bibRefCitation>
). The Hungarian voucher specimen belongs to 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Horstmann" authorityYear="1975" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Nemeritis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="499" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="specularis">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="499">N. specularis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicName authority="Horstmann" authorityName="Horstmann" authorityYear="1975" box="[210,456,476,503]" class="Insecta" family="Ichneumonidae" genus="Nemeritis" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="13" pageNumber="499" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="specularis">
<emphasis box="[210,325,476,502]" italics="true" pageId="13" pageNumber="499">specularis</emphasis>
Horstmann
